sub_title: Medical Oncologist working as Medical Director at prIME Oncology
summary:
I am Medical Director at prIME Oncology for 10+ years. I create and oversee the delivery of programs across a wide range of malignancies for a variety of educational formats, both live and online. As a physician, I understand the ‘’Art of Oncology’’ and clinicians’ needs for practical advice on how to integrate latest advances in individual patient management. I collaborate with world-renown multidisciplinary experts in Oncology and I strive that educational programs are high quality and helpful for practicing clinicians. For 10 years I was the curator of prIME Oncology’s blog posts & newsletter (prIME LINES) that twice weekly provide physicians with some latest Oncology news.
Previously I worked for more than a decade as a medical oncologist at the Institute of Oncology in Ljubljana, Slovenia. I was involved in patient care, clinical cancer research and education of residents, medical students and other health care providers.
